Package containing all classes which are important for the gui.

    Enum Description
    GUIElement.UpdateType
    Type of update which is called on each GUIElement.

Package gui Description

Package containing all classes which are important for the gui. This pachage contains basic gui elements, e.g. GUIController, super class GUIElement, other classes which are used in the package and different other packages containing a fxml file and the corresponding controller.
